15
00:02:02,270 --> 00:02:04,150
-小心點  -抱歉  親愛的
- Watch it! - Sorry, darling.

16
00:02:05,930 --> 00:02:08,020
-給  -謝謝
- Here you are. - Thank you.

17
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:47,870
我可以坐這嗎
Mind if I join you?

18
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:50,160
和他的一樣
I'll have the same.

19
00:02:56,050 --> 00:02:58,790
自我介紹下  我叫甘道夫
I should introduce myself. My name is Gandalf.

20
00:03:00,230 --> 00:03:01,330
灰袍巫師甘道夫
Gandalf the Grey.

21
00:03:02,070 --> 00:03:03,240
我聽說過你
I know who you are.

22
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:07,700
碰到你真巧
Well, now, this is a fine chance.

23
00:03:09,300 --> 00:03:13,220
什么風把索林·橡木盾吹來了布里
What brings Thorin Oakenshield to Bree?

24
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:17,000
我收到消息
I receive words

25
00:03:17,100 --> 00:03:21,580
有人看到我父親在登蘭德荒野游蕩
that my father have been seen wandering in the wilds near Dunland.

26
00:03:23,010 --> 00:03:26,810
我去找過  但一無所獲
I went looking, found no sign of him.

27
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:30,130
索林  很久以來
Thorin, it's been a long time since anything

28
00:03:30,130 --> 00:03:32,440
瑟萊因的消息都只是謠言
but rumor was heard of Thrain.

29
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:35,820
他還活著  我敢保證
He still lives, I am sure of it.

30
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:43,280
我父親失蹤前拜訪過你
My father came to see you before he went missing.

31
00:03:43,870 --> 00:03:45,190
你對他說了什么
What did you say to him?

32
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:48,240
我敦促他進軍艾雷博
I urged him to march upon Erebor.

33
00:03:48,450 --> 00:03:51,070
集合矮人的七支大軍
To gather the seven armies of dwarves.

34
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:55,220
消滅惡龍  收復孤山
To destroy the dragon and take back the Lonely Mountain.

35
00:03:55,410 --> 00:04:00,460
我也要同樣敦促你  去收復家園
And I would say the same to you, take back your homeland.

36
00:04:04,350 --> 00:04:07,770
你不是碰巧遇到我吧  甘道夫
This is no chance meeting, is it, Gandalf?

37
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,770
不
No.

38
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:11,850
不是
It is not.

39
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:15,370
孤山一直困擾著我  索林
The Lonely Mountain troubles me, Thorin.

40
00:04:15,370 --> 00:04:17,900
惡龍盤踞得太久
That dragon has sat there long enough.

41
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:22,810
會引來更加邪惡的力量
Sooner or later, darker minds will turn towards Erebor.

42
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:28,000
我順綠色大道南下時  遇到了些討厭的生物
I ran into some unsavory characters whilst travelling along Greenway.

43
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:30,690
把我當成了流浪漢
They mistook me for a vagabond.

44
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,590
他們肯定后悔了
I imagine they regreted that.

45
00:04:32,590 --> 00:04:34,890
他們還帶了個信
One of them was carrying a message.

46
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,180
這是黑語言[魔多語]fsIt is Black Speech.

47
00:04:42,230 --> 00:04:45,630
-這是懸賞  -懸賞什么
- He promised as payment. - For what?

48
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:48,290
你的人頭
Your head.

49
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:52,150
有人想要你死
Someone wants you dead.

50
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:56,460
索林  你不能再等了
Thorin, you could wait no longer,

51
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:59,130
你是杜林王座的繼承人
you are the heir to the throne of Durin.

52
00:04:59,470 --> 00:05:01,680
召集矮人軍隊
Unite the armies of the Dwarves.

53
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:05,810
齊心協力  去奪回艾雷博
Together you have the might and power to retake Erebor.

54
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:08,510
召集七大矮人家族的會議
Summon a meeting of the seven Dwarf families,

55
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,770
要求他們信守誓言
demand they stand by their oath.

56
00:05:10,770 --> 00:05:12,500
七大家族的軍隊
The Seven Armies sworn an oath to the one

57
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:16,220
只效忠手握阿肯寶鉆的人
who wields the King's Jewel, the Arkenstone.

58
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,360
只有帝王珍寶才能聯合他們
It is the only thing that will unite them,

59
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:21,700
而且  那寶石已經被斯矛革偷走了
and in case you have forgotten, that jewel was stolen by Smaug.

60
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:28,790
如果我幫助你找回它呢
What if I were to help you reclaim it?

61
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:35,310
怎么找  寶石遠在半個中土世界之外
How? The Arkenstone lies half a world away,

62
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:37,860
在那只火龍的魔掌中
buried beneath the feet of a fire-breathing dragon.

63
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:39,520
對
Yes.

64
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,990
所以我們需要一個盜賊
Which is why we're going to need a burglar.

65
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:48,700
{\pos(192.604,214.382)}12個月后

66
00:06:32,910 --> 00:06:39,210
{\pos(226.415,116.494)}斯矛革荒原

67
00:06:43,930 --> 00:06:46,230
-半獸人狼群有多遠  -非常近
- How close is the pack? - Too close.

68
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:48,010
{\an8}一里格=3英里

69
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:48,010
只有幾里格
Couple of leagues, no more.

70
00:06:48,010 --> 00:06:49,090
但還有更要命的
But that's not the worst of it.

71
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,410
他們會嗅到我們的氣味的
They will smell us, pick our scent.

72
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:51,830
現在還沒  不過遲早會的
Not yet but they will do.

73
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:52,950
我們還有別的麻煩
We have another problem.

74
00:06:52,950 --> 00:06:54,220
他們看見你了嗎
Did they see you?

75
00:06:54,370 --> 00:06:56,270
-看見了你嗎  -不  不是這個
- They saw you? - No. That's not it.

76
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:59,290
我怎么說的  安靜得像只老鼠
What did I tell you? Quiet as a mouse.

77
00:06:59,430 --> 00:07:00,990
天生是塊盜賊的料
Excellent burglar material.

78
00:07:00,990 --> 00:07:03,780
聽我說  都聽我說話
Would you listen? Will you just listen?

79
00:07:03,780 --> 00:07:07,040
我要說的是  外面還有其他東西
I'm trying to tell you there is something else out there.

80
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:12,660
它什么樣子  像頭熊嗎
What form did it take, like a bear?

81
00:07:14,030 --> 00:07:16,540
對  但更大  大得多
Yes, but bigger, much bigger.

82
00:07:17,450 --> 00:07:19,390
你認識那野獸嗎
You knew about this beast?

83
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,020
我覺得應該原路返回
I say we double back.

84
00:07:22,020 --> 00:07:24,090
那會被獸人追上的
We will be run down by a pack of wolves.

85
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:28,940
有棟房子  離這不遠
There is a house, it's not far from here,

86
00:07:28,950 --> 00:07:32,150
可供我們躲避
where we might take refuge.

87
00:07:32,150 --> 00:07:33,580
誰的房子
Whose house?

88
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:37,290
-是敵是友  -都不是
- A friend or foe? - Neither.

89
00:07:38,420 --> 00:07:42,590
他也許會幫助我們  也許會殺了我們
He will help us, or, he will kill us.

90
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:45,080
我們還有其他選擇嗎
What choice do we have?

91
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:48,730
沒有
None.

92
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,560
這邊  快跑
This way, quickly!

93
00:08:09,820 --> 00:08:11,190
走
Move!

94
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:14,210
快點
Come on.

95
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:20,670
進房子里
In the house!

96
00:08:22,650 --> 00:08:24,030
快跑
Run!

97
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:33,490
快點  進去
Come on, get inside.

98
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,120
打開門
Open the door!

99
00:08:48,190 --> 00:08:49,330
快點
Quickly.

100
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:01,320
用力推
Push!

101
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,160
快點
Come on!

102
00:09:11,260 --> 00:09:12,680
那是什么
What is that?

103
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,350
我們的房主
That is our host.

104
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:21,780
他叫貝榮
His name is Beorn.

105
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:26,150
他是個變形人
And he's a skin-changer.

106
00:09:27,870 --> 00:09:30,230
有時是頭壯碩的黑熊
Sometimes he's a huge black bear,

107
00:09:30,230 --> 00:09:32,850
有時是個高大強壯的男人
sometimes he's a great strong man.

108
00:09:32,850 --> 00:09:36,820
黑熊喜怒無常  但變成人  他還是講道理的
The bear is unpredictable, but the man can be reasoned with.

109
00:09:36,820 --> 00:09:41,000
不過  他不太喜歡矮人
However, he's not over fond of Dwarves.

110
00:09:43,810 --> 00:09:47,300
-他走了  -離門遠一點
- He's leaving. - Come away from there!

111
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,940
它不正常  這都不正常
It's not natural, none of it!

112
00:09:50,220 --> 00:09:53,570
他肯定被黑魔法控制了
It's obvious, he's under some dark spell.

113
00:09:53,570 --> 00:09:57,100
別犯傻  那是他自己的變形術
Don't be a fool. He's under no enchantment but his own.

114
00:09:57,920 --> 00:10:01,020
好了  現在  大家休息吧
All right, now. Get some sleep, all of you.

115
00:10:01,020 --> 00:10:03,450
今晚你們在這兒是安全的
You'll be safe here tonight.

116
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:08,810
但愿
I hope.

117
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:27,690
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}現在就進攻

118
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:31,110
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}趁矮人渣滓睡著時殺光他們

119
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,320
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}不

120
00:10:36,110 --> 00:10:38,200
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}那頭野獸在站崗

121
00:10:44,660 --> 00:10:47,830
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}我們要在半路上截殺他們

122
00:10:59,340 --> 00:11:02,390
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}大軍正在多爾戈多集結

123
00:11:03,010 --> 00:11:06,810
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}主人召見你

124
00:11:59,270 --> 00:12:02,180
至尊戒  馭眾戒
Ash nazg durbatuluk

125
00:12:03,230 --> 00:12:06,230
至尊戒  尋眾戒
Ash nazg gimbatul

126
00:12:07,450 --> 00:12:10,690
至尊魔戒引眾戒
Ash nazg thrakatuluk

127
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:16,140
黑暗之中鎖眾戒
Agh burzum-ishi krimpatul

128
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:52,980
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}我們人數日漸增長

129
00:12:53,290 --> 00:12:56,000
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}力量日漸增強

130
00:12:56,290 --> 00:12:58,710
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}你來統領軍隊吧

131
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:01,700
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}橡木盾怎么辦

132
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:08,340
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}戰火將至

133
00:13:08,540 --> 00:13:10,480
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}你說我可以取他的人頭

134
00:13:11,580 --> 00:13:13,510
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}凡人終有一死

135
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:20,690
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}還要追殺他們嗎

136
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:26,490
{\pos(190.189,249.978)}博格

137
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,630
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}我有任務給你

138
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:47,380
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}還想喝矮人的血嗎

139
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:54,270
你就是那個橡木盾
So you are the one they call Oakenshield.

140
00:14:54,930 --> 00:15:00,470
告訴我  為什么褻瀆者阿佐格要追殺你
Tell me, why is Azorg the Defiler hunting you?

141
00:15:00,590 --> 00:15:04,010
你認識阿佐格  怎么回事
You know of Azorg. How?

142
00:15:04,010 --> 00:15:07,500
我的族人最先在山中定居
My people were the first to live in the mountains.

143
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:11,420
遠在獸人南下之前
Before the Orcs came down from the north.

144
00:15:11,420 --> 00:15:14,540
褻瀆者幾乎殺光了我的家人
The Defiler killed most of my family.

145
00:15:15,190 --> 00:15:17,620
只留了幾個做奴隸
But some he enslaved.

146
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:20,510
不是做苦力  明白嗎
Not for work, you understand?

147
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:22,060
是為了娛樂
But for sport.

148
00:15:23,540 --> 00:15:28,670
他似乎覺得折磨變形人是種消遣
Caging skin-changers and torturing them seemed to amuse him.

149
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:31,850
還有像你這樣的人嗎
There are others like you?

150
00:15:33,230 --> 00:15:34,930
曾經有很多
Once there were many.

151
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:37,170
現在呢
And now?

152
00:15:38,290 --> 00:15:40,270
只剩一個了
Now there's only one.

153
00:15:42,730 --> 00:15:47,360
你們要在秋天結束前抵達孤山
You need to reach the mountain before the last days of autumn.

154
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:50,680
對  在杜林之日前
Before Durin's Day falls, yes.

155
00:15:50,680 --> 00:15:52,580
你們沒多少時間了
You're running out of time.

156
00:15:52,580 --> 00:15:55,120
所以我們必須穿過黑森林
Which is why we must go through Mirkwood.

157
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,960
有陰影籠罩著黑森林
A darkness lies upon that forest.

158
00:15:58,180 --> 00:16:01,580
邪惡在林間滋生
Foul things creep beneath those trees.

159
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:05,090
墨瑞亞的獸人和多爾戈多的亡靈法師
There is an alliance between the Orcs of Moria

160
00:16:05,090 --> 00:16:08,180
結成了同盟
and the Necromancer in Dol Guldur.

161
00:16:08,290 --> 00:16:12,340
我不會冒險去那里  除非迫不得已
I would not venture there, except in great need.

162
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:16,020
我們走精靈之路  那里再安全不過
We will take the Elven road. That path is too safe.

163
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:17,360
安全
Safe?

164
00:16:17,540 --> 00:16:20,660
木精靈與其他精靈不同
The Wood-elves in Mirkwood are not like their kin.

165
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:24,220
他們沒那么睿智  卻更加危險
They're less wise and more dangerous.

166
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:27,490
但這不重要
But it matters not.

167
00:16:29,290 --> 00:16:30,450
什么意思
What do you mean?

168
00:16:30,450 --> 00:16:34,110
這片土地到處都是獸人
These lands are crawling with Orcs.

169
00:16:34,110 --> 00:16:36,660
他們的數量越來越多
Their numbers are growing.

170
00:16:37,010 --> 00:16:42,730
你們徒步前行  永遠到不了森林的
And you're on foot, you will never reach the forest alive.

171
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:49,480
我不喜歡矮人
I don't like Dwarves.

172
00:16:50,470 --> 00:16:54,630
他們貪婪又盲目
They are greedy, and blind.

173
00:16:54,640 --> 00:16:59,880
瞧不起他們眼中的劣等生物
Blind to the lives of those they deem lesser than their own.

174
00:17:06,570 --> 00:17:09,060
但我更恨獸人
But Orcs I hate more.

175
00:17:10,620 --> 00:17:12,140
你們需要什么
What do you need?

176
00:17:17,340 --> 00:17:19,960
快走吧  趁著天色還早
Go now, while you have the light.

177
00:17:21,010 --> 00:17:23,450
追殺你們的人就在后面
Your hunters are not far behind.

178
00:17:47,350 --> 00:17:49,470
精靈之門
The Elven Gate.

179
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:53,750
這就是去往黑森林的路
Here lies our path through Mirkwood.

180
00:17:53,850 --> 00:17:57,700
沒有獸人的蹤跡  算我們走運
No sign of the Orcs. We have luck on our side.

181
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:09,450
把馬匹放走  讓它們去找主人
Set the ponies loose. Let them return to their master.

182
00:18:11,610 --> 00:18:13,480
這座森林好像
This forest feels...

183
00:18:14,580 --> 00:18:15,710
病了
sick.

184
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:18,530
像是被疾病困擾
As if there's a disease lies upon it.

