I would like to know who you are.

553
01:01:01,790 --> 01:01:03,800
又在這里做些什么事情
And what you are doing in these lands.

554
01:01:03,800 --> 01:01:06,860
我們是從藍山來的商人
We are simple merchants from the Blue Mountains.

555
01:01:06,860 --> 01:01:10,250
要去鐵丘陵走親戚
Journeying to see our kin in the Iron Hills.

556
01:01:11,480 --> 01:01:13,460
你們說是普通商人
Simple merchants you say.

557
01:01:13,940 --> 01:01:17,200
我們需要食物  補給和武器
We need food, supplies, weapons.

558
01:01:17,560 --> 01:01:18,740
你能幫忙嗎
Can you help us?

559
01:01:23,480 --> 01:01:25,580
我知道這些木桶是哪來的
I know where these barrels came from.

560
01:01:26,230 --> 01:01:27,350
怎么了
What of it?

561
01:01:27,350 --> 01:01:30,140
我不知道你們和精靈之間發生了什么
I don't know what business you had with the Elves.

562
01:01:30,730 --> 01:01:32,610
但我覺得結果不太妙
But I don't think it ended well.

563
01:01:34,130 --> 01:01:36,830
除非城主帶路  沒有人進得了長湖城
No one enters Lake-town but by lead of The Master.

564
01:01:37,310 --> 01:01:40,620
他的收入全靠和林地王國的交易
All his wealth comes from trades with the Woodland Realm.

565
01:01:40,620 --> 01:01:42,550
他肯定會把你們扔進牢房
He would see you in irons

566
01:01:42,550 --> 01:01:44,330
不敢招惹瑟蘭迪爾國王
before risking the wraith of king Thranduil.

567
01:01:49,380 --> 01:01:52,230
我打賭肯定有悄悄進城的方法
I'll wager there are ways to enter that town unseen.

568
01:01:52,920 --> 01:01:54,170
對
Aye.

569
01:01:55,490 --> 01:01:59,420
但要有個走私販幫忙
But for that, you would need a smuggler.

570
01:01:59,420 --> 01:02:01,510
我們會付錢的  雙倍
For which we will pay, double.

571
01:02:10,030 --> 01:02:12,470
邪惡就是如此愚蠢
Such is the nature of evil.

572
01:02:13,090 --> 01:02:18,030
即使遍布中土  依舊閉塞盲目
Out there in the vast ignorance of the world it festers and spreads.

573
01:02:18,110 --> 01:02:21,050
有陰影在黑暗中成長
A shadow that grows in the dark.

574
01:02:21,460 --> 01:02:23,110
那惡靈晝夜不休
A sleepless malice

575
01:02:23,120 --> 01:02:26,420
如夜幕一般黑暗
as black as the oncoming wall of night.

576
01:02:27,510 --> 01:02:32,360
之前是這樣  以后也永遠會這樣
So it ever was. So will it always be.

577
01:02:33,470 --> 01:02:37,470
最后  所有的邪惡都會現身
In time, all foul things come forth.

578
01:02:37,480 --> 01:02:40,540
你們在追殺13個矮人
You were tracking a company of 13 Dwarves.

579
01:02:40,560 --> 01:02:41,590
為什么
Why?

580
01:02:41,590 --> 01:02:43,070
不是13個
Not 13.

581
01:02:43,420 --> 01:02:44,710
不再是了
Not any more.

582
01:02:45,500 --> 01:02:48,970
那個年輕人  黑頭發的弓箭手
The young one, the black-haired archer.

583
01:02:49,540 --> 01:02:52,160
他中了魔窟的箭
We stuck him of a Morgul shaft.

584
01:02:53,230 --> 01:02:57,960
毒液滲入血液  他活不長了
Poison is in his blood, he'll be choking on it soon.

585
01:02:58,390 --> 01:03:00,320
回答問題  渣滓
Answer the question, filth.

586
01:03:00,420 --> 01:03:03,170
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}狗沒有權利問我問題  母精靈

587
01:03:05,580 --> 01:03:07,930
最好別惹怒她
I would not antagonize her.

588
01:03:07,990 --> 01:03:10,080
你喜歡殺戮嗎  獸人
You like killing things, Orc?

589
01:03:10,990 --> 01:03:12,340
你喜歡死亡嗎
You like death?

590
01:03:13,990 --> 01:03:15,060
那就讓你嘗嘗死亡的滋味
Then let me give it to you!

591
01:03:15,060 --> 01:03:16,220
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}夠了

592
01:03:16,590 --> 01:03:18,430
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}塔睿爾  走開

593
01:03:18,960 --> 01:03:20,230
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}馬上

594
01:03:30,860 --> 01:03:35,260
我不在乎矮人的死活  回答我的問題
I do not care about one dead Dwarf. Answer the question.

595
01:03:35,670 --> 01:03:37,020
沒什么好害怕的
You have nothing to fear.

596
01:03:38,360 --> 01:03:41,550
把知道的都說出來  我就放你自由
Tell us what you know and I will set you free.

597
01:03:42,050 --> 01:03:44,530
有人要殺死他們  為什么
You had orders to kill them, Why?

598
01:03:44,530 --> 01:03:47,020
索林·橡木盾對你們有什么用
What is Thorin Oakenshield to you?

599
01:03:47,020 --> 01:03:50,430
那個矮冬瓜永遠別想當國王
The Dwarf runt will never be king.

600
01:03:50,430 --> 01:03:52,700
國王嗎  沒有山下之王
King? There's no King Under the Mountain.

601
01:03:52,700 --> 01:03:57,260
將來也不會有  只要那頭龍還活著
Nor will there ever be. None would they enter Erebor

602
01:03:57,260 --> 01:03:58,730
沒人進得去艾雷博
whilst the dragon lives.

603
01:03:58,730 --> 01:04:00,470
你知道什么
You know nothing.

604
01:04:00,520 --> 01:04:03,300
你們的世界將化為火海
Your world will burn.

605
01:04:03,300 --> 01:04:04,980
你在說什么
What are you talking about?

606
01:04:05,360 --> 01:04:06,720
快說
Speak!

607
01:04:07,280 --> 01:04:09,910
我們的時代又回來了
Our time has come again.

608
01:04:10,530 --> 01:04:14,470
我的主人效忠于他
My master serves the One.

609
01:04:15,190 --> 01:04:20,130
現在明白了吧  精靈  死亡就要到來了
Do you understand now, Elfling? Death is upon you.

610
01:04:20,130 --> 01:04:24,710
戰火就要蔓延到這了
The flames of war are upon you.

611
01:04:27,420 --> 01:04:28,530
你為什么這么做
Why did you do that?

612
01:04:28,530 --> 01:04:30,400
你說過要放他自由
You promised to set him free.

613
01:04:30,840 --> 01:04:32,190
我照做了
And I did.

614
01:04:33,030 --> 01:04:36,890
我解放了他那卑鄙的頭顱
I freed his wretched head from his miserable shoulders.

615
01:04:38,200 --> 01:04:40,530
這獸人嘴里還能套出話來
There was more the Orc could tell us.

616
01:04:40,810 --> 01:04:43,300
我覺得沒什么價值了
There was nothing more he could tell me.

617
01:04:43,840 --> 01:04:46,680
他說的戰火是什么意思
What did he mean by the flames of war?

618
01:04:47,030 --> 01:04:49,800
他們要使用什么武器
It means they intend to unleash a weapon

619
01:04:49,800 --> 01:04:51,880
這武器強大到可以毀滅一切
so great it will destroy all before it.

620
01:04:52,720 --> 01:04:56,140
邊境  道路和河流的守衛通通加倍
I want the watch doubled at our borders, all roads, all rivers.

621
01:04:56,140 --> 01:04:58,300
一有動靜  立即稟報
Nothing moves that I hear of it.

622
01:04:58,300 --> 01:05:02,710
嚴禁任何人進出
No one enters this kingdom, and no one leaves it.

623
01:05:05,830 --> 01:05:07,400
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}關閉城門

624
01:05:07,700 --> 01:05:10,970
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}國王下令封城

625
01:05:11,610 --> 01:05:12,840
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}那塔睿爾怎么辦

626
01:05:15,540 --> 01:05:16,980
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}她怎么了

627
01:05:17,140 --> 01:05:18,450
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}她帶著弓箭和匕首

628
01:05:19,350 --> 01:05:21,210
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}跑進森林里去了

629
01:05:21,620 --> 01:05:23,220
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}還沒有回來

630
01:05:46,840 --> 01:05:48,840
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}矮人的血

631
01:05:49,080 --> 01:05:50,380
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}他們經過這里

632
01:05:50,840 --> 01:05:53,680
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}還有另一股味道

633
01:05:57,480 --> 01:05:59,290
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}是人肉

634
01:06:03,360 --> 01:06:06,360
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}他們找到渡湖的方法了

635
01:06:28,030 --> 01:06:29,210
小心點
Watch out!

636
01:06:38,260 --> 01:06:40,510
你干什么  想淹死我們嗎
What are you trying to do? Drown us?

637
01:06:40,510 --> 01:06:43,200
這片水域生養了我  矮人老爺
I was born and bred on these waters , master Dwarf.

638
01:06:43,390 --> 01:06:46,700
就算我想淹死你們  也不會選這里
If I wanted to drown you, I would not do it here.

639
01:06:48,530 --> 01:06:51,300
我受夠這個長湖城的滑頭了
Oh, I've had enough of this slippy lake-man.

640
01:06:51,300 --> 01:06:54,100
要我說直接丟掉他  甩了他
I say we throw him over the sail and then we dump him.

641
01:06:54,200 --> 01:06:56,450
巴德  他叫巴德
Bard, his name is Bard.

642
01:06:56,460 --> 01:06:57,380
你怎么知道的
How do you know?

643
01:06:57,380 --> 01:06:59,000
我問的
Um, I asked him.

644
01:06:59,000 --> 01:07:02,030
我才不管他叫什么  我不喜歡他
I don't care what he calls himself, I don't like him.

645
01:07:02,030 --> 01:07:05,570
我們不需要喜歡他  付錢給他就行
We do not have to like him. We simply have to pay him.

646
01:07:05,570 --> 01:07:08,560
來吧伙計  錢都拿出來
Come now lads, turn out your pockets.

647
01:07:09,670 --> 01:07:11,600
我們怎么知道他不會背叛我們
How do we know he won't betray us?

648
01:07:11,600 --> 01:07:12,900
不知道
We don't.

649
01:07:13,980 --> 01:07:16,600
還有個大問題
There's um, still a big problem.

650
01:07:17,210 --> 01:07:19,100
還差10枚銀幣
We're 10 coins short.

651
01:07:20,880 --> 01:07:25,230
葛羅音  快點  把你的錢拿出來
Gloin, come on. Give us what you have.

652
01:07:25,230 --> 01:07:26,830
找我干什么
Don't look to me.

653
01:07:26,960 --> 01:07:30,990
這次冒險弄得我傾家蕩產
I've been bled dry by this venture.

654
01:07:31,060 --> 01:07:34,020
一點回報都沒見到
What have I seen from my investment?

655
01:07:34,420 --> 01:07:37,820
什么都沒有  只有痛苦和悲傷
Naught but misery and grief and...

656
01:07:45,880 --> 01:07:47,880
老天爺啊
Bless my beard.

657
01:07:48,490 --> 01:07:51,750
拿去  全都拿走
Take it, take all of it.

658
01:07:56,280 --> 01:07:57,650
錢呢  快點給我
The money, quick, give it to me.

659
01:07:57,650 --> 01:07:59,420
拿到供給之后自然會付你錢
We will pay you when we get our provisions,

660
01:07:59,420 --> 01:08:00,150
否則不行
but not before.

661
01:08:00,150 --> 01:08:02,860
不想被關進大牢  就聽我的
If you value your freedom, you'll do as I say.

662
01:08:03,180 --> 01:08:04,840
前面有守衛
There are guards ahead.

663
01:08:22,840 --> 01:08:24,220
他在干什么
What's he doing?

664
01:08:24,790 --> 01:08:26,420
他在和什么人說話
He's talking to someone.

665
01:08:28,190 --> 01:08:30,480
還對著我們指指點點
He's pointing right at us.

666
01:08:33,410 --> 01:08:34,870
現在握起手來了
Now they're shaking hands.

667
01:08:34,870 --> 01:08:35,570
什么
What?

668
01:08:35,570 --> 01:08:36,490
這個壞人
The villain!

669
01:08:36,490 --> 01:08:38,160
他把我們賣了
He's selling us out.

670
01:09:00,850 --> 01:09:01,960
安靜
Quiet!

671
01:09:04,860 --> 01:09:06,520
馬上到城門關了
We're approaching the tollgate.

672
01:09:17,740 --> 01:09:22,450
停船  貨物檢查  請出示文書
Halt. Goods inspection. Papers, please.

673
01:09:23,440 --> 01:09:24,770
原來是你啊  巴德
Oh, it's you, Bard.

674
01:09:24,780 --> 01:09:25,890
早上好  珀西
Morning, Percy.

675
01:09:25,890 --> 01:09:27,520
有什么要申報的嗎
Anything to declare?

676
01:09:27,520 --> 01:09:31,840
沒有  我又累又冷  想趕緊回家
Nothing, that I am cold and tired, and ready for home.

677
01:09:31,840 --> 01:09:33,450
我也是
You and me both.

678
01:09:37,270 --> 01:09:39,810
給你  沒問題了
Here we are, all in order.

679
01:09:39,810 --> 01:09:43,400
別著急
Not so fast.

680
01:09:43,530 --> 01:09:48,470
從林地王國托運回來的空木桶
Consignment of empty barrels from the Woodland Realm.

681
01:09:48,780 --> 01:09:53,030
怎么不是空的呢
Only, they are not empty,

682
01:09:54,100 --> 01:09:55,220
巴德
are they, Bard?

683
01:09:55,440 --> 01:09:59,690
沒記錯的話  你的執照是駁船工
If I recall correctly. Your licensed as a bargeman.

684
01:10:00,090 --> 01:10:04,020
而不是漁夫
Not a fisherman.

685
01:10:04,150 --> 01:10:05,830
不關你的事
That's none of your business!

686
01:10:05,840 --> 01:10:10,820
錯了  這關城主的事  也就是我的事
Wrong. It's the Master's business, which makes it my business.

687
01:10:10,820 --> 01:10:13,230
拜托  埃弗雷德  講點情理  城民等著吃飯呢
Oh, come on, Alfred, Have a heart. People need to eat!

688
01:10:13,820 --> 01:10:16,470
這些魚是非法的
These fish are illegal.

689
01:10:17,210 --> 01:10:19,020
-把桶清空  -快點
- Empty the barrels over the side. - You heard him.

690
01:10:19,430 --> 01:10:21,070
倒進河里
In the canal.

691
01:10:22,090 --> 01:10:23,100
快點
Come on.

692
01:10:24,320 --> 01:10:26,210
鎮上的人民在挨餓
Folks in this town are struggling.

693
01:10:26,630 --> 01:10:29,230
日子艱難  食物又少
Times are hard, food is scarce.

694
01:10:29,230 --> 01:10:30,840
跟我有什么關系
That's not my problem.

695
01:10:30,910 --> 01:10:34,450
如果人們聽說城主把魚扔進湖里
And when the people hear their Master's dumping the fish in the lake,

696
01:10:34,870 --> 01:10:37,210
掀起暴動的話
when the rioting starts,

697
01:10:39,450 --> 01:10:41,340
跟你有關系了嗎
Will it be your problem, then?

698
01:10:45,560 --> 01:10:47,240
住手
Stop!

699
01:10:50,450 --> 01:10:55,230
充當人民英雄嗎  巴德  平民保護神
Ever the people's champion, aye, Bard? Protector of the common folk.

700
01:10:55,230 --> 01:10:58,510
他們不會一直支持你的  船夫
You might have their favor now, bargeman. But it won't last.

701
01:11:01,930 --> 01:11:03,660
把門打開
Raise the gate.

702
01:11:06,160 --> 01:11:10,070
別忘了  城主盯著你呢
The Master has his eye on you, you do well to remember.

703
01:11:10,070 --> 01:11:11,650
我們知道你住哪里
We know where you live.

704
01:11:11,650 --> 01:11:16,380
地方這么小  埃弗雷德  大家可都知根知底
It's a small town, Alfred. Everyone knows where everyone lives.

705
01:11:32,700 --> 01:11:35,020
外面的動靜很大
All these talks of civil are unrest.

706
01:11:35,020 --> 01:11:37,340
有人在煽風點火  大人
Someone's been stirring the pot, Sire.

707
01:11:40,170 --> 01:11:41,620
痛風了嗎  大人
Gout playing ox, Sire?

708
01:11:41,630 --> 01:11:46,050
是潮氣  肯定是潮氣  給我弄點白蘭地
It's the damp, it's the only possible explanation. Get me a brandy.

709
01:11:46,520 --> 01:11:49,370
大人  民眾的情緒讓人不快
The mood of the people, sire, is turning ugly.

710
01:11:49,370 --> 01:11:52,800
平民就這樣  埃弗雷德  讓人不愉快
They're commoners, Alfred. They've always been ugly.

711
01:11:52,810 --> 01:11:57,340
這地方到處是魚腥臭氣  又不怪我
It's not my fault that they live in a place that stinks of fish oil and tar.

712
01:11:57,910 --> 01:11:59,720
工作  房屋
Jobs, shelter,

713
01:11:59,720 --> 01:12:03,030
食物  只有這點追求
food, that's all they ever plead about.

714
01:12:03,030 --> 01:12:07,100
大人  肯定有人在幕后指使
It is my belief, sire, that they've been led on by trouble makers.

715
01:12:07,800 --> 01:12:11,710
那就給我找出來  逮捕他們
Then we must find these trouble makers, and arrest them.

716
01:12:11,800 --> 01:12:13,810
我也是這么想的  大人
My thoughts exactly, sire.

717
01:12:13,810 --> 01:12:17,280
改革的言論給我壓下去
And all these talks of change must be supressed.

718
01:12:17,360 --> 01:12:21,070
絕對不能讓造反的人聚在一起  制造言論
What a fault to let the rebel banded together and start making noises.

719
01:12:21,070 --> 01:12:26,030
搞不好他們還要問責  成立委員會
The next thing you know, they'll start asking questions, forming commities...

720
01:12:27,200 --> 01:12:28,870
發起調查
launching inquiries.

721
01:12:28,870 --> 01:12:31,930
舊的不去  新的不來
Out with the old, in with the new.

722
01:12:32,000 --> 01:12:33,090
什么
What?

723
01:12:33,300 --> 01:12:35,480
我一直都在這么說  大人
That's what I've been saying, sire.

724
01:12:35,600 --> 01:12:37,780
還有傳言說要選舉
There's even talk of election.

725
01:12:37,780 --> 01:12:42,730
選舉  真荒唐  我絕不允許
Election? It's absurd. I won't stand for it.

726
01:12:43,820 --> 01:12:46,440
他們不需要您允許吧  大人
I don't think they'll ask you to stand, sire.

727
01:12:48,200 --> 01:12:52,190
這些強盜  忘恩負義  還想造反
Sackers, ingrates, rebel-rousers.

728
01:12:52,190 --> 01:12:55,770
誰敢質疑我的權威
Who would have the nerve to question my authority!

729
01:12:55,770 --> 01:12:58,450
誰敢  誰
Who would dare? Who...

730
01:13:03,180 --> 01:13:04,710
巴德
Bard.

731
01:13:05,520 --> 01:13:10,420
絕對沒錯  幕后黑手就是這個船夫
You mark my words, that trouble-making bargeman is behind all this.

732
01:13:18,290 --> 01:13:19,910
別碰我
Get your hands off me.

733
01:13:26,570 --> 01:13:28,860
你沒見過他們  他們沒來過這里
You didn't see them. They were never here.

734
01:13:30,240 --> 01:13:31,910
魚送你了
Fish you can have for nothing.

735
01:13:34,870 --> 01:13:36,000
跟上我
Follow me.

736
01:13:44,920 --> 01:13:49,320
爸  我們的房子被監視了
Da, our house, it's being watched.

737
01:14:24,860 --> 01:14:27,080
告訴城主我今天辦完事了
You can tell the Master I'm done for the day.

738
01:14:28,190 --> 01:14:29,330
爸
Da.

739
01:14:29,700 --> 01:14:30,940
你去哪了
Where have you been?

740
01:14:30,940 --> 01:14:33,870
爸爸  你回來了  我好擔心
Father, there you are! I was worried.

741
01:14:34,270 --> 01:14:37,810
好  貝恩  叫他們出來
Yes. Bain, get them in.

742
01:14:45,360 --> 01:14:49,820
要是你跟別人說  我就把你的胳膊擰下來
If you speak of this to anyone. I'll rip your arms off.

743
01:14:52,480 --> 01:14:53,660
別碰我
Off.

744
01:14:55,130 --> 01:14:56,160
在那邊
Out there.

745
01:15:04,280 --> 01:15:07,490
爸  為什么有矮人從廁所里爬出來
Da, why are the Dwarves climbing out from our toilet?

746
01:15:07,490 --> 01:15:09,050
他們能帶來好運嗎
Will they bring us luck?

747
01:15:13,090 --> 01:15:16,060
可能不是很合身  但是保暖
They may not be the best fit, but they'll keep you warm.

748
01:15:17,040 --> 01:15:18,110
謝謝
Thank you.

749
01:15:28,190 --> 01:15:30,350
矮人風弩
The Dwarvish Windlass.

750
01:15:30,840 --> 01:15:32,770
你像是見了鬼魂一樣
You look like you've seen a ghost.

751
01:15:33,460 --> 01:15:38,080
沒錯  上次見到這武器
Yes. The last time we saw such a weapon,

752
01:15:39,340 --> 01:15:41,410
河谷城化為了灰燼
a city was on fire.

753
01:15:42,240 --> 01:15:44,670
那天巨龍襲來
It was the day the dragon came.

754
01:15:48,050 --> 01:15:50,880
斯矛革摧毀了河谷城
The day that Smaug destroyed Dale.

755
01:15:53,070 --> 01:15:55,420
城主吉利恩
Girion, the Lord of the city.

756
01:15:55,460 --> 01:15:58,300
集結弓箭手射擊巨龍
Rallied his bowman to fire upon the beast.

757
01:15:58,740 --> 01:16:03,380
但龍皮無比堅固  牢不可破
But a dragon's hide is tough. Tougher than the strongest armor.

758
01:16:03,600 --> 01:16:08,500
只有風弩射出的黑箭能夠刺穿
Only a black arrow fired from a Windlass would pierce the dragon hide.

759
01:16:09,530 --> 01:16:12,830
這種箭本就寥寥無幾
And few of those arrows were ever made.

760
01:16:18,010 --> 01:16:22,260
吉利恩背水一戰時  僅剩數支
The store was running low when Girion made his last stand.

761
01:16:29,480 --> 01:16:32,690
哪怕他能射中一箭
Had the aim of men been true that day...

762
01:16:33,360 --> 01:16:35,320
也不會落到這步田地
much would've been different.

763
01:16:39,210 --> 01:16:41,360
難道你當時在場
You speak as if you were there?

764
01:16:42,700 --> 01:16:44,770
所有矮人都知道這個故事
All Dwarves know the tale.

765
01:16:44,910 --> 01:16:47,340
那你應該知道吉利恩擊中了巨龍
And you would know that Girion hit the dragon?

766
01:16:47,510 --> 01:16:49,050
射落了左翼的一塊鱗片
It loosened the scale on the left wing

767
01:16:49,270 --> 01:16:52,030
再補一箭就能殺死那怪物
one more shot he would have killed the beast.

768
01:16:52,840 --> 01:16:56,230
不過是童話而已  孩子  只是童話
That's fairy story, lad. Nothing more.

769
01:16:57,360 --> 01:16:58,770
你收了錢
You took all our money.

770
01:16:59,820 --> 01:17:01,290
武器在哪里
Where are the weapons?

771
01:17:03,600 --> 01:17:04,860
等著
Wait here.

772
01:17:19,370 --> 01:17:21,480
明天是最后一個秋日
Tomorrow begins our last day of autumn.

773
01:17:21,480 --> 01:17:23,840
后天便是杜林之日
Durin's day falls the morning after next.

774
01:17:23,940 --> 01:17:26,150
必須在那之前趕到孤山
We must reach the mountain before then.

775
01:17:26,150 --> 01:17:27,480
如果不能呢
And if we do not?

776
01:17:27,570 --> 01:17:30,400
如果那之前找不到隱秘之門呢
If we fail to find the hidden door before that time?

777
01:17:30,400 --> 01:17:32,300
那計劃就全落空了
Then this quest has been for nothing.

778
01:17:44,420 --> 01:17:45,720
這是什么
What is this?

779
01:17:45,950 --> 01:17:47,290
鉤矛
Pike hook.

780
01:17:47,690 --> 01:17:49,370
舊魚叉改的
Made from an old harpoon.

781
01:17:49,370 --> 01:17:50,120
這個呢
And this?

782
01:17:50,120 --> 01:17:53,090
我們叫它鶴嘴鋤  改進過的鐵匠錘
A crowbill, we call it. Expansion from smittys hammer.

783
01:17:53,240 --> 01:17:54,830
雖然上手很重
It's heavy in hand, I grant.

784
01:17:54,830 --> 01:17:58,330
但需要保命時  也能湊合著用
But in defense of your life, these will serve you better than none.

785
01:17:58,330 --> 01:18:01,080
我們買的是武器
We paid you for weapons.

786
01:18:01,080 --> 01:18:04,380
鐵鑄黑鞘的寶劍
Iron forged, swords of dark sheath.

787
01:18:04,380 --> 01:18:05,630
這是開玩笑
It's a joke.

788
01:18:07,480 --> 01:18:10,140
這是軍械庫外最好的武器了
You won't find better outside the city armory.

789
01:18:10,140 --> 01:18:12,860
鐵鑄的兵器都鎖在軍械庫里
All iron-forged weapons are held there and locked in key.

790
01:18:12,860 --> 01:18:14,310
索林
Thorin.

791
01:18:14,860 --> 01:18:17,070
拿著這些走吧
Why not take his offer and go?

792
01:18:17,070 --> 01:18:19,570
更差的兵器我都用過  你不也是
I've made do with less. So have you.

793
01:18:21,130 --> 01:18:22,420
我們現在就走
I say we leave now.

794
01:18:22,420 --> 01:18:24,130
你們哪都不能去
You're not going anywhere.

795
01:18:24,210 --> 01:18:25,270
你看到什么了
What did you see?

796
01:18:25,270 --> 01:18:29,400
全城的眼線  乃至狼狗都盯著這里
There are spies watching this house and probably every wolf and dog in town.

797
01:18:30,220 --> 01:18:31,990
必須等到傍晚
You must wait until nightfall.

798
01:18:48,260 --> 01:18:49,480
索林
Thorin.

799
01:19:02,530 --> 01:19:03,660
爸
Da?

800
01:19:06,650 --> 01:19:08,090
別讓他們出門
Don't let them leave.

801
01:19:33,370 --> 01:19:35,200
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}我還當你是獸人

802
01:19:35,540 --> 01:19:37,200
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}如果我是獸人

803
01:19:37,500 --> 01:19:38,740
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}你早就死了

804
01:19:40,500 --> 01:19:45,360
不要一個人追殺30個獸人
You can not hunt 30 orcs on your own.

805
01:19:45,630 --> 01:19:47,380
可我不是一個人
But I'm not on my own.

806
01:19:48,300 --> 01:19:49,880
你知道我要跟來
You knew I would come?

807
01:19:52,290 --> 01:19:54,370
國王很憤怒  塔睿爾
The king is angry, Tauriel.

808
01:19:54,390 --> 01:19:57,900
600年來  我父親一直保護你  寵愛你
For 600 years, my father has protected you, favored you.

809
01:19:58,240 --> 01:19:59,530
你卻違抗了他的命令
You defied his orders.

810
01:19:59,540 --> 01:20:01,500
辜負了他的信任
You betrayed his trust.

811
01:20:02,980 --> 01:20:04,360
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}跟我回去

812
01:20:04,360 --> 01:20:06,110
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}他會原諒你的

813
01:20:06,250 --> 01:20:07,750
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}但我不會

814
01:20:07,880 --> 01:20:10,820
{\pos(188.981,249.978)}如果跟你回去  我不會原諒自己

815
01:20:11,350 --> 01:20:13,880
國王從未準許獸人入境
The king has never let Orcs fill from outlands.

816
01:20:14,120 --> 01:20:16,050
這次卻縱容他們穿越邊境
But he would let this Orc pack cross our borders

817
01:20:16,230 --> 01:20:17,430
追殺我們的犯人
and kill our prisoners.

818
01:20:17,820 --> 01:20:20,610
-我們不該插手  -怎么不該插手
- It is not our fight. - It is our fight.

819
01:20:21,440 --> 01:20:25,930
他們不會善罷甘休  這是在助長邪惡
It will not end here. With every victory this evil will grow.

820
01:20:26,430 --> 01:20:29,160
如果你父親一意孤行  我們袖手旁觀
If your father has his way, we would do nothing.

821
01:20:29,400 --> 01:20:34,020
我們只能躲在城墻后  不見天日
We will hide within our walls, live our lives away from light.

822
01:20:34,390 --> 01:20:36,190
任由黑暗侵襲
And let the darkness descend.

823
01:20:37,740 --> 01:20:39,530
我們不是中土世界的一員嗎
Are we not a part of this world?

824
01:20:40,870 --> 01:20:45,540
<i>朋友</i>  怎么能讓邪惡力量比我們強大
Tell me <i>mellon</i>, when did we let evil become stronger than us?

825
01:20:50,670 --> 01:20:52,820
你好  巴德  你在找什么
Hello, Bard. What you after?

826
01:20:54,330 --> 01:20:58,310
有一條舊掛毯  上哪去了
There was a tapestry, an old one. Where has it gone?

827
01:20:58,610 --> 01:20:59,910
什么舊掛毯
What tapestry are you talking about?

828
01:21:00,680 --> 01:21:01,740
這條
This one.

829
01:21:02,200 --> 01:21:05,000
告訴你  他們是矮人  憑空出現的
They were Dwarves, I tell you. Appeared out of nowhere.

830
01:21:05,210 --> 01:21:09,090
滿臉胡子  瞇縫眼  從來沒見過
Full-beards, pierced eyes. I've never seen the like.

831
01:21:09,410 --> 01:21:11,330
矮人在這做什么
What are Dwarves doing in these parts?

832
01:21:11,720 --> 01:21:12,740
是預言
It's the prophecy.

833
01:21:12,960 --> 01:21:16,280
-預言  -杜林后人的預言
- Prophecy? -Prophecy of Durin's folk.

834
01:21:24,890 --> 01:21:26,070
預言
Prophecy?

835
01:21:29,930 --> 01:21:30,890
預言
Prophecy.

836
01:21:31,120 --> 01:21:32,670
那些傳說可能成真了
The old tales may come true.

837
01:21:32,960 --> 01:21:35,100
大筆財寶
Vast hordes of treasure?

838
01:21:35,370 --> 01:21:36,520
是真的嗎
Can it really be true?

839
01:21:36,830 --> 01:21:39,270
銀泉之主回歸了嗎
Has the Lord of the silver fountains returned?

840
01:21:39,980 --> 01:21:45,420
銀泉之主  刻石之王
The lord of the silver fountains. The king of carven stone.

841
01:21:46,920 --> 01:21:48,160
山下之王
The King Beneath the Mountain.

842
01:21:49,900 --> 01:21:51,560
將重回寶座
Shall come into his own.

843
01:21:53,180 --> 01:21:57,300
人民歡慶山下之王的回歸
And the bell shall ring in gladness at the Mountain King's return.

844
01:21:58,020 --> 01:22:00,480
但一切必以悲劇收場
But all shall fail in sadness,

845
01:22:01,210 --> 01:22:03,940
湖水閃耀  戰火重燃
and the lake will shine and burn.

846
01:22:06,370 --> 01:22:09,170
-爸  我想阻止他們  -他們走了多久
- Da, I tried to stopped them... - How long have they been gone?

847
01:22:15,670 --> 01:22:18,120
拿到武器  直接去孤山
As soon we have the weapons we make straight for the Mountain.

848
01:22:18,640 --> 01:22:19,520
快  快  快
Go, go, go.

849
01:22:38,960 --> 01:22:39,760
你還好嗎
You all right?

850
01:22:40,310 --> 01:22:41,420
撐得住
I can manage.

851
01:22:42,440 --> 01:22:43,730
我們趕緊走吧
Let's just get out of here.

852
01:22:58,270 --> 01:22:59,280
快跑
Run!

853
01:23:28,300 --> 01:23:30,400
這什么意思
What is the meaning of this?

854
01:23:30,860 --> 01:23:32,610
抓到他們在偷武器  大人
We caught them stealing weapon, sire.

855
01:23:33,530 --> 01:23:35,480
這是全民公敵呀
Enemies of the state, em?

856
01:23:35,810 --> 01:23:38,890
看樣子是群下賤的傭兵  大人
A disgrace bunch of mercenaries, if ever there were, Sire.

857
01:23:39,080 --> 01:23:40,180
住嘴
Hold your tongue!

858
01:23:43,110 --> 01:23:45,340
你不知道你在跟誰講話
You do not know to whom you speak.

859
01:23:45,790 --> 01:23:49,160
這哪是什么犯罪  他是索林
This is no common criminal! This is Thorin,

860
01:23:49,470 --> 01:23:52,620
瑟羅爾的后人  瑟萊因之子
son of Thrain, son of Thror!

861
01:23:55,740 --> 01:23:57,390
我們是艾雷博的矮人
We are the Dwarves of Erebor.

862
01:24:00,550 --> 01:24:03,380
我們來收復故土
We have come to reclaim our homeland.

863
01:24:08,480 --> 01:24:10,990
我還記得這鎮子昔日的輝煌
I remember this town in the great days of old.

864
01:24:12,710 --> 01:24:14,540
碼頭停滿了船舶
Fleets of boats laid at the harbor,

865
01:24:14,790 --> 01:24:17,040
滿載絲綢和珠寶
filled with silks and fine gems.

866
01:24:17,560 --> 01:24:19,780
這里不是被人遺忘的湖邊小城
This was no forsaken town on a lake.

867
01:24:20,400 --> 01:24:24,150
這里曾是北方的貿易中心
This was the center of all trade of the North.

868
01:24:25,940 --> 01:24:27,540
我要重現往日的輝煌
I would see those days return,

869
01:24:28,030 --> 01:24:30,020
點亮矮人的熔爐
I would relive the great forges of Dwarves,

870
01:24:30,670 --> 01:24:33,130
讓艾雷博的商隊
send wealth and riches flowing once more...

871
01:24:33,520 --> 01:24:34,670
載滿財富接踵而來
from the hordes of Erebor!

872
01:24:37,620 --> 01:24:41,010
你只會帶來死亡
Death, that is what you will bring upon us.

873
01:24:42,580 --> 01:24:44,880
龍火和毀滅
Dragon fire and ruin.

874
01:24:46,720 --> 01:24:50,550
吵醒了那怪物  我們就全完了
If you awaken that beast, it will destroy us all.

875
01:24:51,010 --> 01:24:54,320
你們可以聽他勸阻  不過我保證
You can listen to this nay-sayer, but I promise you this:

876
01:24:57,160 --> 01:24:58,350
如果成功
If we succeed,

877
01:25:00,020 --> 01:25:02,510
孤山的財富大家可以一起分享
all will share in the wealth of the Mountain.

878
01:25:06,990 --> 01:25:11,330
到手的財富  可以讓十個埃加洛斯重現輝煌
You will have enough gold, to rebuild Esgaroth 10 times over.

879
01:25:13,320 --> 01:25:16,940
所有人  聽我說  聽好
All of you, listen to me! You must listen!

880
01:25:17,230 --> 01:25:19,140
你們忘記河谷城的事了嗎
Have you forgotten what happened in Dale?

881
01:25:21,250 --> 01:25:24,010
忘記葬身火海的百姓了嗎
Have you forgotten of those who died in firestorm?

882
01:25:26,510 --> 01:25:27,910
都是為了什么
And for what purpose?

883
01:25:29,160 --> 01:25:31,500
為了山下之王盲目的野心
The blind ambition of a Mountain King.

884
01:25:31,660 --> 01:25:35,450
貪婪蒙蔽了他的雙眼  他心里只有欲望
So riven by greed, he can not see beyond his own desire!

885
01:25:37,000 --> 01:25:40,810
等一等  我們每個人
No, no. We must not, any of us,

886
01:25:41,070 --> 01:25:43,600
都不要急著橫加指責
be too quick to lay blame.

887
01:25:44,520 --> 01:25:47,580
不要忘了  吉利恩
Let us not forget, that it was Girion,

888
01:25:47,860 --> 01:25:50,900
河谷城主  你的先人
Lord of Dale, your ancestor,

889
01:25:51,270 --> 01:25:53,340
沒能殺死那怪物
who failed to kill the beast.

890
01:25:56,260 --> 01:25:59,610
沒錯  大人  我們都知道這個故事
It's true, sire. We all know the story.

891
01:26:00,570 --> 01:26:05,480
他射了一箭又一箭  卻全部射偏
Arrow after arrow he shot, each one missing its mark.

892
01:26:12,460 --> 01:26:13,740
你無權
You have no right,

893
01:26:15,410 --> 01:26:17,250
無權進入孤山
no right to enter that mountain.

894
01:26:19,230 --> 01:26:20,930
只有我有權利
I have the only right.

895
01:26:27,490 --> 01:26:30,040
請問長湖城主
I speak to the Master of the men of the lake.

896
01:26:30,790 --> 01:26:32,530
您愿意見證預言成真嗎
Will you see the prophecy fulfilled?

897
01:26:34,090 --> 01:26:35,250
愿意
Will you...

898
01:26:35,630 --> 01:26:39,490
分享我們的無盡財富嗎
share in the great wealth of our people?

899
01:26:44,210 --> 01:26:45,350
您怎么說
What say you?

900
01:26:49,510 --> 01:26:54,710
我要說  歡迎
I say unto you, welcome!

901
01:26:55,650 --> 01:27:00,790
請平身  歡迎山下之王
Welcome and rise! Welcome, King under the mountain!

902
01:27:12,750 --> 01:27:14,220
你知道我們少一個人吧
You do know we have one short?

903
01:27:14,440 --> 01:27:16,810
-比弗在哪  -他不在也不要管他
- Where's Bifur? - He's not here, we leave him behind.

904
01:27:17,090 --> 01:27:20,030
