Something you carry.

1092
01:53:06,280 --> 01:53:09,460
是金子做的
Something made of gold.

1093
01:53:09,910 --> 01:53:16,140
卻比金子珍貴
But far more precious.

1094
01:53:20,170 --> 01:53:25,280
在這呀  躲躲藏藏的小偷
There you are, a thief in the shadows.

1095
01:53:27,210 --> 01:53:29,690
我沒想偷東西
I did not come to steal from you.

1096
01:53:29,980 --> 01:53:33,630
