我翻山越嶺  跋山涉水
And under hills and over hills, my path is lead.

1115
01:54:52,620 --> 01:54:56,830
來去無蹤的我  穿梭到了這里
And, and through the air. I am here that He walks unseen.

1116
01:54:56,830 --> 01:55:01,710
