I am...

1118
01:55:05,850 --> 01:55:07,180
好運隨身的人
luck-wearer...

1119
01:55:08,850 --> 01:55:13,800
-猜謎能手  -好名號  繼續
- Riddle-maker. - Lovely titles, go on.

1120
01:55:13,960 --> 01:55:16,500
-酒桶騎士  -酒桶
- Barrel-rider. - Barrels.

1121
01:55:16,770 --> 01:55:18,660
